attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: OFFER ACCEPTED AND OH CANCELLED!! This expansive townhome, nestled on a peaceful street just moments from the best of South Boston, offers over 2,000 SF of luxurious living space. Built in 2015, the property is completely move-in ready and includes TWO GARAGE PARKING SPACES. The open-concept floor plan is perfect for modern living, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and beautiful hardwood floors throughout. The spacious living and dining area, complete with a gas fireplace and surround sound, is ideal for entertaining, while the chef's kitchen impresses with a large waterfall island and top-of-the-line appliances. The primary suite is a true retreat, offering ample closet space and a sleek en-suite bathroom with a double vanity and radiant floor heating. The offering includes an in-unit washer/dryer and 2 additional bedrooms plus a versatile bonus space, currently used as a home gym. Step outside to enjoy one of the many outdoor spaces, including a private patio and a roof deck!
